---
/**
 * rest-api/0005 · Figure 4 — "deprecation timeline · announce → overlap → retire".
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from docs/rest-api/lessons/0005-api-versioning-strategies.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption incl. the footnote <sup>). Lives as an .astro
 * component, NOT inline in the MDX, because MDX's JSX parser is unreliable with
 * raw inline SVG that uses kebab-case attributes.
 *
 * The source SVG references the arrowhead marker (arw) that the source page
 * defines ONCE in a body-level <svg><defs> block shared by all four figures. To
 * keep this figure self-contained and rendering byte-for-byte, that marker is
 * embedded here in a local <defs> (id + fill unchanged so url(#arw) resolves).
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 168"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Evolution timeline: v1 live, then deprecate with Deprecation and Sunset headers while v2 runs in parallel, then retire after usage drains"
    >
        <defs>
            <marker
                id="arw"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
            >
        </defs>
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="320"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">DEPRECATION TIMELINE · ANNOUNCE → OVERLAP → RETIRE</text
            >
            <!-- timeline rail -->
            <line x1="20" y1="84" x2="620" y2="84" stroke="#d8d4c8" stroke-width="2"></line>
            <!-- v1 live -->
            <rect x="20" y="60" width="150" height="48" rx="9" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
            ></rect>
            <text x="95" y="80" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-weight="700" fill="#2f5d3a"
                >v1 LIVE</text
            >
            <text x="95" y="97" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e">sole surface</text
            >
            <line x1="170" y1="84" x2="190" y2="84" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <!-- deprecate / overlap -->
            <rect
                x="192"
                y="36"
                width="226"
                height="96"
                rx="9"
                fill="#fbfaf2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="305"
                y="54"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">DEPRECATE · run in parallel</text
            >
            <rect x="204" y="62" width="202" height="22" rx="5" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="305"
                y="77"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="8.5"
                font-family="ui-monospace,Menlo,monospace"
                fill="#7a2218">Deprecation: true</text
            >
            <rect x="204" y="88" width="202" height="22" rx="5" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="305"
                y="103"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="8.5"
                font-family="ui-monospace,Menlo,monospace"
                fill="#7a2218">Sunset: Sat, 01 Nov 2025 …</text
            >
            <text x="305" y="124" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >v1 + v2 both serve · months, not days</text
            >
            <line x1="418" y1="84" x2="438" y2="84" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <!-- retire -->
            <rect x="440" y="60" width="180" height="48" rx="9" fill="#f1eee2" stroke="#6b675f"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="530"
                y="80"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">RETIRE v1</text
            >
            <text x="530" y="97" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >only after usage drains</text
            >
            <!-- bottom row of duties -->
            <text x="320" y="152" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#1f3a5a"
                >In-band headers (RFC 8594) + out-of-band changelog/email/docs · <tspan
                    font-weight="700"
                    fill="#7a1f12"
                    >monitor real traffic, then remove — not on a calendar guess.</tspan
                ></text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        <code>Deprecation</code> + <code>Sunset</code> (RFC 8594) ride in every response so even silent
        clients carry the warning; you sunset only once real usage on v1 has genuinely drained.<sup
            ><a href="#s4" id="r4">4</a></sup
        >
    </figcaption>
</figure>
